headline: Evergy Announces 2024 Results, Declares Quarterly Dividend, Reaffirms 2025 Guidance
summary: KANSAS CITY, Mo., February 27, 2025--Evergy, Inc. (NASDAQ: EVRG) today announced full year 2024 GAAP earnings of $873.5 million, or $3.79 per share, compared to GAAP earnings of $731.3 million, or $3.17 per share, for the full year 2023. Fourth quarter 2024 GAAP earnings were $78.2 million, or $0.34 per share, compared to earnings of $58.0 million, or $0.25 per share, for the fourth quarter of 2023.
